---
import HomePanel from './HomePanel.astro';
import SectionRule from './SectionRule.astro';
---

<HomePanel id="how" screenLabel="How it works">
  <SectionRule num="04" left="How it works" right="From setup to first plan" />
  <div class="collab-top">
    <div class="section-head reveal" style="margin:0">
      <h2 class="display">Onboarding that fits<br /><span class="accent">around your planning decisions.</span></h2>
      <p>From an empty workspace to a plan your team can act on – collaborative, not a long enterprise rollout.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="collab-time reveal" data-delay="1">
      <div class="ct-num"><span class="accent">2–3</span> hrs</div>
      <div class="ct-lbl">Hands-on working session</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flow flow--panel reveal">
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="fdot"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="20" height="20"><rect x="4" y="5" width="16" height="14" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M4 9h16M9 5v14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/></svg></div>
      <span class="fnum">01</span><h4>Scope it together</h4><p>Define what's in scope, the priority categories, and the goal you're planning toward.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="fdot"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="20" height="20"><ellipse cx="12" cy="6" rx="7" ry="2.6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M5 6v12c0 1.4 3.1 2.6 7 2.6s7-1.2 7-2.6V6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7"/></svg></div>
      <span class="fnum">02</span><h4>Bring your data in</h4><p>Connect master data, measures, demand drivers, and stock.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="fdot"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="20" height="20"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      <span class="fnum">03</span><h4>Read the signal together</h4><p>Review data quality and confirm the drivers that move your numbers.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="fdot"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="20" height="20"><path d="M4 18l5-7 4 3 7-9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      <span class="fnum">04</span><h4>Apply the right intelligence</h4><p>Demand, inventory, or supply – run the algorithms that fit your needs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="fdot"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="20" height="20"><path d="M6 21V4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M6 5h12l-2.6 3.4L18 12H6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
      <span class="fnum">05</span><h4>Decide and move</h4><p>Adjust assumptions, challenge the numbers, own the call. The decision is yours.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</HomePanel>
